%% Package / Module Structure — ModelRouter (Gradle multi-module)
graph TD
    Root["modelrouter (root)"]

    Root --> Ingress[router-ingress]
    Root --> CoreMod[router-core]
    Root --> SPI[router-provider-spi]
    Root --> CacheMod[router-cache]
    Root --> AdminMod[router-admin]
    Root --> SecurityMod[router-security]
    Root --> ObsMod[router-observability]
    Root --> DashboardMod[router-dashboard]
    Root --> AdaptersRoot[provider-adapters]
    Root --> SDKs[sdk]

    CoreMod --> CorePolicy["core.policy<br/>PolicyResolver, RoutingPolicy<br/>PolicyStore port"]
    CoreMod --> CorePlanner["core.planner<br/>CandidateEnumerator<br/>ProviderScorer<br/>RoutingStrategy + built-ins"]
    CoreMod --> CoreExecution["core.execution<br/>ExecutionEngine<br/>CircuitBreakerRegistry<br/>ResponseNormalizer<br/>RetryPolicy engine"]

    AdaptersRoot --> POpenAI[provider-openai]
    AdaptersRoot --> PAnthropic[provider-anthropic]
    AdaptersRoot --> PGemini[provider-gemini]
    AdaptersRoot --> POllama[provider-ollama]
    AdaptersRoot --> PBaseten[provider-baseten]
    AdaptersRoot --> PVLLM[provider-vllm]
    AdaptersRoot --> PGroq[provider-groq]
    AdaptersRoot --> PFireworks[provider-fireworks]
    AdaptersRoot --> PTogether[provider-togetherai]
    AdaptersRoot --> PAzure[provider-azure-openai]

    SDKs --> SDKJava[sdk-java]
    SDKs --> SDKAndroid[sdk-android]

    CoreMod -.depends on.-> SPI
    Ingress -.depends on.-> CoreMod
    POpenAI & PAnthropic & PGemini & POllama & PBaseten & PVLLM & PGroq & PFireworks & PTogether & PAzure -.implements.-> SPI
    CacheMod -.used by.-> CoreExecution
    SecurityMod -.used by.-> Ingress
    ObsMod -.instruments.-> Ingress
    ObsMod -.instruments.-> CoreMod
    AdminMod -.publishes config to.-> CorePolicy
    DashboardMod -.calls.-> AdminMod
    SDKJava & SDKAndroid -.calls REST/gRPC.-> Ingress

    CorePolicy -.policy.-> CorePlanner
    CorePlanner -.ranked candidates.-> CoreExecution

